    <div class="footer-top">
        <div>
            <div class="footer-logo">🛍️ ShopEasy</div>
            <p class="footer-brand">India's favourite online shopping destination. Premium products, unbeatable prices, and fast delivery straight to your door. Shop with confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Quick Links</h4>
